Tomek,

see R-admin C.3.5.1: https://cran.r-project.org/doc/manuals/r-patched/R-admin.html#Accelerate
so essentially just add the following to the regular flags:
--enable-BLAS-shlib --with-blas='-framework Accelerate'

Cheers,
Simon




